{"id":288294,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/04/维权网-各地在京访民召开维权之路研讨会（图）/","date":"2013-04-08T19:16:08Z","modified":"2013-04-08T19:16:08Z","title":"维权网 | 各地在京访民召开维权之路研讨会（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员唐韵报道）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>日</span><span>，来自全国各地的上访维权人士自发聚集到一起，召开一次别开生面的研讨会。与会的三十多位维权者认为：走维权之路首先要团结，大家团结一致反腐才有力量。同时也痛斥劫访这种“怪相”。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>吉林邓志波说：“访民维权之路怎么走，地方对上访维权案件搞三级信访终结，国家敏感时期访民就被监控、打压、拘留、教养，访民本身就是弱势群体，不团结起来就不能有力的去反腐”。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>上海吴玉芬说：“访民走上维权之路就没有退路，通过网络向各界媒体呼吁，关注我们中国的人权状况”。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>北京徐香玉说：“我是北京人，我打赢了官司政府还是不解决问题。大家来自各地上访维权已经很不容易了，没有地方住的可以到我家里来，我尽微薄之力帮一把”。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>天津郑建慧说“我们维权这么多年，就是案件到了最高法院照样违反程序办案。手持最高法院通知书的司法难民，抗议法院、政府以低廉的价钱私聊，要求依法纠正错案——追责！”</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>甘肃曹瑞霞说：“母亲是医疗事故，案子胜诉后父亲到法院领判决被法院付院长殴打致腿部骨折。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>岁时就和弟弟曹小龙一起上访，已经</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span><span>年了，各个信访口去过无数次，没用。希望大家团结起来，俗话说，官向官、民向民。大家一起去中纪委，监察部”。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>山西彭静梅，广西曹建国，吉林张丽云，江苏邵允黎，辽宁刘莉，赵广军等纷纷发言。大家表示一定团结起来共同反腐，维权到底！</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-WkDPFC2PzWk/UWLg-p5LG2I/AAAAAAAAgDk/OPppjm5R6uo/s1600/%E7%A0%94%E8%AE%A8%E4%BC%9A.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"226\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-WkDPFC2PzWk/UWLg-p5LG2I/AAAAAAAAgDk/OPppjm5R6uo/s320/%E7%A0%94%E8%AE%A8%E4%BC%9A.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-iPj3-lt6_nI/UWLg_zzf02I/AAAAAAAAgDs/gJ8crnjeqAc/s1600/%E4%BC%9A1.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-iPj3-lt6_nI/UWLg_zzf02I/AAAAAAAAgDs/gJ8crnjeqAc/s320/%E4%BC%9A1.JPG\" width=\"190\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-fINcxlv0cVs/UWLhCaze_UI/AAAAAAAAgD0/xb_A5HlNOZU/s1600/%E4%BC%9A.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"256\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-fINcxlv0cVs/UWLhCaze_UI/AAAAAAAAgD0/xb_A5HlNOZU/s1600/%E4%BC%9A.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br /></span></div>\n</div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=2ea93c5b7b\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/msuvD\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,20534],"tags":[19196]}